{"abstract":[{"text":"±7° in radians — the yaw turn-pose gate (","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"yawLeft"},{"text":" \/ ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"yawRight"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"static","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"yawThreshold","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Double","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sd"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Narrowed in stages (±15° → ±10° → ±8° → ±7°): users reported having","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to “turn a lot” before a turn pose accepted. Vision’s yaw estimate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"compresses the physical rotation (the same effect documented for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pitch below, milder on yaw), and at large physical turns Vision"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"often drops yaw to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" — which disables the blind-Vision time"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"fallback (a readable angle was seen earlier in the pose), so the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pose can only clear via the ~10 s stall cap. Opening the matched"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"window at ±7° lets the hold accumulate at a smaller, more reliably"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"readable angle. Still clears the ±5° "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"front"},{"type":"text","text":" zone with a 2° margin."}]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEO